mental results are presented\nand rigorous mathematical stability analysis are provided. These results will\nbe particularly useful for aggressive load transportation that involves large\ndeformation of the cable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Aug 2015 04:08:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-18"}
